Class Lecture

java.lang.Object
com.ehab.urs.Lecture
public class Lecture extends Object
The `Lecture` class represents a lecture session for a specific section of a course. It includes information about the start and end time, day, room, section, credits, and lecture duration. The class provides methods to access and modify lecture details and a formatted string representation of the lecture.

2023-12-21
